name: Graffiti Street Art
prompt: A VibeDeck controller covered in graffiti street art. Spray paint tags, drips, and wild style lettering covering every surface. Bright clashing colors - pink, yellow, electric blue, orange. The rotary knob has a cartoon character face painted on it. Stickers and wheat paste texture. Urban, rebellious, artistic. Looks like it was customized by a street artist. Gritty concrete background with more graffiti.
why: Urban culture, artistic expression, youth appeal
